			<h1 class="storytitle"><a href="http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/?p=167" rel="bookmark">Marela is open&#8230;well, kind of</a></h1>

			<div class="post-text">
				<p><a href="http://www.marela.si">Marela</a> is accepting new members. Only by invitation for now, but it&#8217;s not that difficult to get one. Just <a href="http://markos.gaivo.net">email me</a>, if you&#8217;d like one.</p>
<p>For the curious ones, who&#8217;d like to avoid registration, it&#8217;s best described as <a href="http://www.flickr.com">Flickr</a> lite for slovenians (and those who don&#8217;t mind the language). It will grow in its own direction, hopefully fast, but you have to start somewhere.</p>
<p>Those, who like programming might also check out its <a href="http://www.marela.si/dev/api" title="Link to API">API</a>. And if you have any questions, do ask me or <a href="http://www.trepca.si/blog/" title="Link to Sebastjan's blog">Sebastjan</a>.</p>
			</div>

